22:41.777 --> 22:43.320
[gasps]

22:44.321 --> 22:46.406
No! No!

22:46.907 --> 22:52.662
It is not a long-lost  mantilla  from Spain
that nearly ripped the family apart!

22:55.499 --> 22:56.500
I should call Mirtha.

22:58.043 --> 22:58.877
Meh.

23:02.839 --> 23:05.217
-Alex...
-What'd I do now?

23:05.801 --> 23:06.885
Everything.

23:08.470 --> 23:11.139
[breathes deeply] We just saw your  papi.

23:11.765 --> 23:14.768
He said you were trying to mend things
between him and your sister.

23:15.852 --> 23:17.521
Yeah. I guess I did that.

23:18.605 --> 23:19.898
Building bridges.

23:21.483 --> 23:24.778
You know,  Papi  even said
you called him a typical cisgender male.

23:25.862 --> 23:28.448
-I couldn't be more proud.
-[chuckles softly]

23:29.032 --> 23:31.034
So, is everything cool with you guys now?

23:31.118 --> 23:35.455
Mmm... I don't know if we're cool,
but we're talking. That's a start.

23:36.498 --> 23:38.041
Come here. [chuckles]

23:38.125 --> 23:39.543
[Penelope and Elena sigh]

