23:49.094 --> 23:50.762
You better get used to this.

23:51.471 --> 23:52.764
I love you, dumdum!

23:52.848 --> 23:54.558
See, this makes me so happy.

23:54.641 --> 23:56.435
I couldn't stand seeing you
